### PR-011

**Title**: Audit log of configuration changes, key rotations, and combo edits
**Problem**: Compliance requirements (SOC2, ISO 27001) need an audit trail. None exists. The `src/lib/audit` directory has only high-level action icons, not a true audit subsystem.
**Solution**:
- New subsystem in `src/lib/audit/store.ts` with append-only NDJSON store plus optional SQLite (using `better-sqlite3`) for queryability. Records: `actor`, `action`, `target`, `before`, `after`, `ip`, `user_agent`, `request_id`, `timestamp`.
- API `GET /api/audit?actor=...&action=...&since=...&until=...` with pagination.
- UI page `src/app/(dashboard)/audit/page.tsx` with filter chips, diff view, CSV export.
- Files affected: `src/lib/audit/store.ts` (new, 260 LOC), `src/lib/audit/types.ts` (new, 80 LOC), `src/lib/audit/middleware.ts` (new, 110 LOC), `src/lib/audit/sinks/sqlite.ts` (new, 160 LOC), `src/lib/audit/sinks/file.ts` (new, 90 LOC), `src/app/api/audit/route.ts` (new, 180 LOC), `src/app/api/audit/[id]/route.ts` (new, 90 LOC), `src/app/(dashboard)/audit/page.tsx` (new, 220 LOC), `src/app/(dashboard)/audit/DiffView.tsx` (new, 130 LOC), `src/app/(dashboard)/audit/FilterChips.tsx` (new, 100 LOC), `src/lib/auth/middleware.ts:1-180` (mount audit hook on PATCH/POST/DELETE), `tests/unit/audit/store.test.ts` (new, 250 LOC), `tests/e2e/audit/audit.spec.ts` (new, 160 LOC), `docs/security/01-audit.md` (new, 100 LOC).
**Test plan**: Perform 50 CRUD ops via API, query `/api/audit`, assert ordering, before/after diffs. Replay a sample event to verify immutability.
**Risk**: Med â€” PII in audit logs; redact before persisting.
**Estimate**: L

